# bonkbot-dashboard - Synthesized Context

## Discovery Summary
- **First discovered**: 2026-01-10
- **Last updated**: 2026-01-10
- **Discovery depth**: Standard
- **Documentation quality**: Basic (README focuses on deployment)

---

## System Identity

**What it is**: Internal admin dashboard for BonkBot operations.

**What it does**:
- Manages users, DAOs, notifications, and referrals
- Handles VIP status and partnership tiers
- Creates/manages referral codes
- Broadcasts notifications to users

**Key insight**: Critical ops tool for internal team - manages production user data.

---

## Architecture Highlights

### Stack
- Backend: Fastify (Node.js)
- Frontend: Next.js
- Database: PostgreSQL (bonkbot production)
- Auth: Google Cloud Secrets
- Deployment: Docker + tmux on GCP VMs

### Structure
```
backend/          # Fastify API server
frontend/         # Next.js admin UI
deploy-*.sh       # Deployment scripts
*-compose.yaml    # Docker configs
```

---

## Key Capabilities

| Feature | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| User Management | VIP status, account flags |
| DAO Management | DAO creator permissions |
| Referral Codes | Create/manage codes |
| Notifications | Broadcast to users |

---

## Working Here

### Deploy
```bash
# SSH to GCP
gcloud compute ssh --zone "europe-west4-c" "internal-tool" --project "bonkbot-core-prod"

# Deploy
sudo bash deploy-prod.sh
```

